12. Rb1 fxg3 13. hxg3 Bg4
{ Pinning the knight on f3 so that the pawn on e5 cannot be taken. } 14. Rd6
Nbd7 15. c5
{ If White attacks the bishop on g4 with  15.Nh2  , Black will first attack the rook with  15...Ne8  and after this rook moves back, Black will play  16.--  Be6  . }
15... Rfe8
