{ Withdrawing the bishop to g7 is not so great because why would we give White the option of Ng5? Black has time but eventually, the queen needs to go to f7, the knight to c5 and the a-rook to e8, the exact order is less important. }
16. Ba3 b6
{ Black is fine as the only weakness, the pawn on e7, is well-protected and someday ...e7-e5 will solve all the problems. }
