Kh8
{ And although the position is still equal, White needs to play precisely to maintain the balance. Black can quickly become better either via a kingside attack and/or putting the knight on c5 or even via e6 @@StartBracket@@after fxg6 has been played@@EndBracket@@ to d4. }
