15. Ned5
{ If White takes  15.Qxb7  , the queen will get in danger after  15...Bc6  followed by ...Qd7. }
15... Bd7 { White was threatening e2-e3 followed by Ne6. } 16. Be3 Nf5
{ Black has a fine position and can hope for more in the long term with the pair of bishops. }
