18. Be2 { White threatens f2-f4. } 18... Qb6
{ Now after f2-f4 and taking the pawn on d6, Black will take the pawn on e3 with check. }
19. Na4 Qa7
{ And Black is OK. We will play ...Rad8 next and it is not clear how White can make progress. }
