{ Possible because the pawn on e3 is protecting both the d4-pawn and the bishop on f4. }
12. Nxe4 Nxe2+ 13. Qxe2 b6
{ Black has already a small advantage based on the two powerful bishops. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
