Rad1 fxg3 18. hxg3 Nxg3
{ The idea of sacrificing the knight on g3 and then giving checks with the queen on e3 and h6 is a recurring theme in multiple Leningrad lines. }
19. fxg3 Rxd6 20. Qxd6 Qe3+ 21. Kh2 Qh6+ 22. Kg1 Qe3+
